31 Aparā enam gṛhītvā agre
32 vicchindantī vastrāṇi udaram adarśayat;
33 tena niryātā duḥsparśena prabuddho 'ham.

34 Aham apāyayām akṣī, tataḥ satguruḥ uvāca, "Trayaḥ
35 śabdāḥ mayā uktaḥ tava!", "Uttiṣṭha, āgaccha ca;
36 prāpnuyāvaḥ praveśadvāram yena tvam praveśitum śaknuyaḥ".

40 Anugacchantam mama śiraḥ āsīt
41 Yathā yasya tadbhāvanābhiyuktam,
42 Yaḥ svayam eva setubandhasya ardhacakram karoti;

58 "Apaśyas", uvāca, "tāṃ purāṇīm abhicāriṇīm
59 yā ekā asmābhiḥ upari adhunā rodate;
60 apaśyas katham naraḥ tayā viyujyate.

61 Basti, caṇḍāni ca bhūmau padadvayam;
62 cakṣuṣī nirikṣasva cakram yad bhramat
63 nityaḥ patiḥ bṛhatbhiḥ cakraiḥ.

85 caakṣuṣī ātmanaḥ prabhoḥ prati cakṣuṣī nyavartayam;
86 yatas tena mama abhilāṣasya darśanam abhyanujñātam
87 yat yat icchati.

106 Mama parivartanaḥ, aham!, tarda āsīt;
107 Yathā ca kṛtaḥ abhavam rājanīyaḥ pālakaḥ,
108 Tathā avajagāma jīvanasya mithyātvam.

109 Apaśyam tatra na śāmyati hṛdayam,
110 Na ca punar āroḍhum śakyate tatra jīvite;
111 Yatas tasya jīvanasya snehaḥ mayi jātaḥ.

112 Yāvad etad avadhi mama jīvaḥ daridrā
113 Devaś ca viyuktaḥ sarvathā lobhinī ca āsīt;
114 Adhunā, yathā tvam paśyasi, atra tayā daṇḍyamānā asmi.

115 Yadaśubham kuryāt kṛpaṇaḥ, tatraiva prakāśyate
116 prāyaścittau jīvānāṃ parivṛttānām;
117 na ca parvataḥ kaścid api daṇḍanam kṛcchrād api atiricyate.

124 pādayoḥ kare ca baddhvā gṛhītvā ca;
125 yāvat ca nyāyyasya īśvarasya priyam bhaviṣyati,
126 tāvat sthāsyāmaḥ acalāḥ vistīrṇāś ca.

139 Gaccha tvam adhunā: na icchāmi yathā tvam adhikaṃ sthāḥ;
140 yataḥ tava sthitiḥ mama rodanam adhikaṃ duḥkhadam karoti,
141 yena parīkṣayāmi yat tvam avocatḥ.

142 Tatrāsti me pautrī yasyāḥ nāma Alagyeti,
143 sā svata eva śubhā, yadi na asmākam kulam
144 tām durācārāṃ karoti;
